61
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:35,839
[SPEAKER_00] I ja sam logičan.

62
00:07:36,839 --> 00:07:40,040
[SPEAKER_00] I meni je to, ja rekao, pa to je istina.

63
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:42,040
[SPEAKER_00] Ali mi je bilo teško.

64
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:43,779
[SPEAKER_00] I bio sam ljut.

65
00:07:43,779 --> 00:07:47,819
[SPEAKER_00] I opet, ajmo reći, veća kriza.

66
00:07:47,819 --> 00:07:52,519
